{"type": "article", "id": 24670, "title": "三个盒子的音响", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-30T07:01:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145816JZRWK9gavxCtrwGH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这三个方形的木盒子是一组音响，是用胡桃木做的，通过上面的线连接起来。胡桃木音响本身是一种怀旧，但将音响分开却是非常新鲜有趣的做法，你可以交换顺序或旋转它，就像是三个积木。带调控功能的音响可以连接电脑或其他电器，设计师来自泰国，他正在众筹这个产品，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/classictone-simple-walnut-speakers#/\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021458149eyLzSd7J816h3pt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145814BO4q3j1h8YoSkbFu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145815cp0OTw2slPCohAue.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145815dTJc61yU7xaFePts.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}